{"lemma":"مِثْقالِ","slug":"مِثْقالِ","root":"ث.ق.ل","root_slug":"ث-ق-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ث-ق-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مِثْقال","root":"ثقل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":8},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4577"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%90%D8%AB%D9%92%D9%82%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"scale"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"weight","examples":[{"text":"إِنَّ اللَّهَ لَا يَظْلِمُ مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ وَإِنْ تَكُ حَسَنَةً يُضَاعِفْهَا وَيُؤْتِ مِنْ لَدُنْهُ أَجْرًا عَظِيمًا","english":"Indeed, Allah does not do injustice, as much as an atom's weight; while if there is a good deed, He multiplies it and gives from Himself a great reward."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mithqal, a certain weight measure in the Arab world of varying value, usually around 4.5 grams"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Tool noun derived from ثَقُلَ (ṯaqula, “to be heavy”)."},"ipa":["/miθ.qaːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4577","headword_ar":"مِثْقَالٌ","root":"vql","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weight"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miyzaAn","text_ar":"مِيزَان"},{"kind":"text","text":", JK, S, K, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wazon","text_ar":"وَزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":", Msb, TA, and Jel in iv. 44 and x. 62 and xxi. 48, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zinap","text_ar":"زِنَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA) of a thing, (JK, S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino mivolihi","text_ar":"مِنْ مِثْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[but why this is added I do not see]); (S, Msb, K;) [i. e.] its"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"equal in weight;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(PS, and Bd in x. 62;) its"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quantity"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miqodaAr","text_ar":"مِقْدَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"). (Bd in xxi. 48.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yaEozubu Eano rab~ika mino","text_ar":"مَا يَعْزُبُ عَنْ رَبِّكَ مِنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mivoqaAli *ar~apK","text_ar":"مِثْقَالِ ذَرَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur x. 62, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not hidden from thy Lord aught of the weight of the smallest ant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jel:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing equal in weight to a small ant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the motes that are seen in a ray of the sun that enters through an aperture."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing with which one weights;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"viqolN","text_ar":"ثِقْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any of the weights of the balance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain weight, of which the quantity is well known;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a dirhem and three sevenths of a dirhem;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mk","text_ar":"مك"},{"kind":"text","text":";) i. e., the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seventh part of ten dirhems:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a dirhem and a half;"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the present day; i. e.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seventy-two sha'eerehs:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Karmánee, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twenty keeráts."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Hidáyeh, TA.) ―         -b4-  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain coin;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diynaArN","text_ar":"دِينَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.; (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dnr","text_ar":"دنر"},{"kind":"text","text":";)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mivoqaAl","text_ar":"مِثْقَال"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of gold:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavaAqiylu","text_ar":"مَثَاقِيلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloqaY Ealayohi mavaAqiylahu","text_ar":"اَلْقَى عَلَيْهِ مَثَاقِيلَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He threw upon him his weight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burden;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maw^uwnatahu","text_ar":"مَوُونَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[perhaps meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the burden of supporting him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Aboo-Nasr, S, K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"viqolN","text_ar":"ثِقْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["JK","S","Msb","K","Jel"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}